            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/12309418/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/12309418/" class="">第11页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/thenic/" class=" " title="无知">无知</a>
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="12309418">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">要学好西方哲学，必须掌握五种语言：希腊文、拉丁文、英文、法文和德文。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2011-04-11 16:04</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">1人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>要学好西方哲学，必须掌握五种语言：希腊文、拉丁文、英文、法文和德文。</q></blockquote>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







